### [Acts Chapter 22](../../../bib/kjv/act022.htm#001.md)

[Acts](../../../bib/kjv/act001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">act 22:0</span></span>

Overview

[Act 22:1](../../../bib/kjv/act022.htm#001.md), Paul declares at large how
he was converted to the faith, [Act
22:17](../../../bib/kjv/act022.htm#017.md). and called to his apostleship;
[Act 22:22](../../../bib/kjv/act022.htm#022.md), At the very mentioning of
the Gentiles the people exclaim on him; [Act
22:24](../../../bib/kjv/act022.htm#024.md), He would have been scourged;
[Act 22:25](../../../bib/kjv/act022.htm#025.md), but claiming the privilege
of a Roman, he escapes.

